# Directions to L100 Stealth Trainer (Cuthbert, mob 6795)

Say { "Hello";
	say Hello %n, what can I do for you chum?;
	}

say { "trainer";
	tell %n Aye, sure I know where he is but....;
	tell %n I can only give you a hint...;
	tell %n The road is long as well it should;
	tell %n To find the one you search for good.;
	tell %n In a tavern silently he waits,;
	tell %n to train you in stealth, aye mate!.;
	pat %n;
	tell %n Northwest of Grimhaven must ye go,;
	tell %n In a land where Huscarls roam.;
	}

